WEBVTT

00:04.227 --> 00:05.511
What you doing?

00:05.513 --> 00:06.645
You said clean up.

00:06.647 --> 00:08.847
I'm cleaning up.

00:10.016 --> 00:11.883
You can't just throw
everything in the closet.

00:11.885 --> 00:13.102
Hey, you can tell me

00:13.104 --> 00:15.821
what to do
or you can tell me how to do it,

00:15.823 --> 00:19.158
but you can't do both;
this isn't sex.

00:20.744 --> 00:22.745
What if someone looks in there?

00:22.747 --> 00:24.279
They're just coming
over for dinner.

00:24.281 --> 00:25.864
No one's gonna
look in the closet.

00:25.866 --> 00:26.999
Well, you don't know that.

00:27.001 --> 00:28.283
What if someone's
looking for the bathroom

00:28.285 --> 00:29.334
and they open that door?

00:29.336 --> 00:30.536
Could work out.

00:30.538 --> 00:31.770
For all we know,

00:31.772 --> 00:33.639
there's a toilet
in there somewhere.

00:33.641 --> 00:35.591
Fine. But after tonight,

00:35.593 --> 00:37.593
we need to get a handle
on this mess.

00:37.595 --> 00:38.711
You know what we should do?

00:38.713 --> 00:39.950
We should show the
closet to Sheldon.

00:39.975 --> 00:40.680
Why?

00:40.681 --> 00:41.880
Are you kidding?

00:41.882 --> 00:43.849
He's like a savant
at organizing.

00:43.851 --> 00:46.018
Everything in his apartment
has a label on it.

00:46.020 --> 00:48.053
Including his label maker,
which has a label

00:48.055 --> 00:49.555
that says "Label Maker."

00:51.274 --> 00:53.308
And if you look really close
at that label maker label,

00:53.310 --> 00:56.428
you'll see a label
that says "Label."

00:56.430 --> 00:58.597
He's our guest;
we can't just ask him

00:58.599 --> 00:59.948
to straighten our closet.

00:59.950 --> 01:02.100
No, we wouldn't ask him.

01:02.102 --> 01:04.620
We'd just show him the closet

01:04.622 --> 01:07.573
and let the goblins in his head
take it from there.

01:08.775 --> 01:10.576
Hey, guys, come on in.

01:10.578 --> 01:11.794
Hi.
Hi.

01:11.796 --> 01:14.296
Ooh, it smells good.
Thanks.

01:14.298 --> 01:16.665
And, Sheldon, I know tonight's
the night you eat Thai food,

01:16.667 --> 01:18.751
so I went to the Asian market,
got all the ingredients

01:18.753 --> 01:19.802
and made it from scratch.

01:19.804 --> 01:21.837
Oh, you shouldn't have.

01:21.839 --> 01:23.338
Oh, it's my pleasure.

01:23.340 --> 01:25.307
No, you really shouldn't have.

01:25.309 --> 01:27.726
I brought my own.

01:27.728 --> 01:30.312
You stopped
and got him takeout?

01:30.314 --> 01:31.313
I had no choice.

01:31.315 --> 01:33.799
He kept kicking
the back of my seat.

01:33.801 --> 01:36.018
Sheldon, I've been
cooking all day.

01:36.020 --> 01:38.737
Well... now don't you
feel silly.

01:40.774 --> 01:42.808
Show him the closet.

